<font color="#FF0000">HAVE WE PROGRESSED?</font><br>
<tt>Fri Nov 29  9:39:03 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
Pat Buchannan is an idiot.  He has not changed or matured.  The role he played and what he said about the proposed Wall and Maya were stupid.  The fact that he can still say and do the same things and still be considered an important figure, makes me sick.  As much as we would like to think we have progressed, we haven't.  Sure more women and minorities are doing things and accomplishing stuff they hadn't been able to do in the past; however, this Nation still has a very dark side, as demonstrated by Buchannan, et al.  <br>
Maya is a hero.  She stood-up to the pressure, held her ground, but more importantly, the Wall has and will remain the most important and touching memorial this Nation has.    
